title: K: Dream of Green
original_name: K -ドリーム・オブ・グリーン-
sinopse: The Green King surrounded by mystery, Hisui Nagare. Kurou's former senior disciple, Mishakuji Yukari. The youth who carries the weight being an executive, Gojou Sukuna. The drunkard and slovenly middle-aged man, Iwafune Tenkei. A manga depicting the daily life of the Green Clan, Jungle, with its abundance of personalities.
